#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.apply.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.apply"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:1 of
msgid "Apply function `func` group-wise and combine the results together."
msgstr "按组应用函数 `func` 并将结果组合在一起。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:3 of
msgid ""
"The function passed to `apply` must take a dataframe as its first "
"argument and return a DataFrame, Series or scalar. `apply` will then take"
" care of combining the results back together into a single dataframe or "
"series. `apply` is therefore a highly flexible grouping method."
msgstr ""
"传递给 `apply` 的函数必须以一个 DataFrame 作为第一个参数，并返回一个 "
"DataFrame、Series 或标量。`apply` 会负责将结果重新组合成一个单独的 "
"DataFrame 或 Series。因此，`apply` 是一种非常灵活的分组方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:9 of
msgid ""
"While `apply` is a very flexible method, its downside is that using it "
"can be quite a bit slower than using more specific methods like `agg` or "
"`transform`. Pandas offers a wide range of method that will be much "
"faster than using `apply` for their specific purposes, so try to use them"
" before reaching for `apply`."
msgstr ""
"虽然 `apply` 是一种非常灵活的方法，但它的缺点是使用起来可能比使用更具体的"
"方法（如 `agg` 或 `transform`）慢很多。Pandas 提供了许多针对特定用途比 `"
"apply` 更快的方法，因此在使用 `apply` 之前应优先尝试这些方法。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.apply.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:15 of
msgid ""
"A callable that takes a dataframe as its first argument, and returns a "
"dataframe, a series or a scalar. In addition, the callable may take "
"positional and keyword arguments."
msgstr ""
"一个可调用对象，其第一个参数为一个 DataFrame，并返回一个 DataFrame、"
"Series 或标量。此外，该可调用对象还可以接受位置和关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:19 of
msgid "Specify type of returned object. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回对象的类型。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:21 of
msgid "Specify dtypes of returned DataFrames. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回 DataFrame 的数据类型。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:23 of
msgid "Specify dtype of returned Series. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回 Series 的数据类型。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:25 of
msgid "Specify name of returned Series. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回 Series 的名称。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:27 of
msgid "Specify index of returned object. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回对象的索引。详见 `Notes`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:29 of
msgid "Whether to infer dtypes when dtypes or output_type is not specified."
msgstr "当未指定 dtypes 或 output_type 时是否推断数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:31 of
msgid ""
"If True, the index of returned dataframe or series will automatically "
"contain group keys if as_index=True, or group indexes if as_index=False, "
"when group_keys=True.  .. note::     `prepend_index_group_keys` will be "
"set to True by default in     future releases, and a warning will be "
"shown if the parameter     is set to False. To make sure your code works "
"in future     releases, please set this to True and remove group indexes"
"     in index parameter or type annotation of `func`."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则当 group_keys=True 时，返回的 DataFrame 或 Series 的索引将"
"自动包含组键（如果 as_index=True）或组索引（如果 as_index=False）。  .. "
"注意::     在未来的版本中，`prepend_index_group_keys` 将默认设置为 True，"
"     如果该参数被设置为 False，将会显示警告。为了确保您的代码在未来的版本"
"中正常工作，     请将其设置为 True，并在索引参数或 `func` 的类型注解中"
"移除组索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:31 of
msgid ""
"If True, the index of returned dataframe or series will automatically "
"contain group keys if as_index=True, or group indexes if as_index=False, "
"when group_keys=True."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则当 group_keys=True 时，返回的 DataFrame 或 Series 的索引将"
"自动包含组键（如果 as_index=True）或组索引（如果 as_index=False）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:36 of
msgid ""
"`prepend_index_group_keys` will be set to True by default in future "
"releases, and a warning will be shown if the parameter is set to False. "
"To make sure your code works in future releases, please set this to True "
"and remove group indexes in index parameter or type annotation of `func`."
msgstr ""
"`prepend_index_group_keys` 在未来的版本中将默认设置为 True，如果该参数被"
"设置为 False，将会显示警告。为了确保您的代码在未来的版本中正常工作，请将"
"其设置为 True，并在索引参数或 `func` 的类型注解中移除组索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:42
#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:44 of
msgid "Optional positional and keyword arguments to pass to `func`."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的可选位置和关键字参数。"

