msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:52 of
msgid ":py:obj:`pipe`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:53 of
msgid "Apply function to the full GroupBy object instead of to each group."
msgstr "将函数应用于整个 GroupBy 对象，而不是每个组。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:55 of
msgid ":py:obj:`aggregate`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:56 of
msgid "Apply aggregate function to the GroupBy object."
msgstr "将聚合函数应用于 GroupBy 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:58 of
msgid ":py:obj:`transform`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:59 of
msgid "Apply function column-by-column to the GroupBy object."
msgstr "将函数逐列应用于 GroupBy 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:61 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.apply`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:62 of
msgid "Apply a function to a Series."
msgstr "将函数应用于 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:64 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.apply`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:65 of
msgid "Apply a function to each row or column of a DataFrame."
msgstr "将函数应用于 DataFrame 的每一行或每一列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:68 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:69 of
msgid ""
"When deciding output dtypes and shape of the return value, MaxFrame will "
"try applying ``func`` onto a mock grouped object, and the apply call may "
"fail. When this happens, you need to specify the type of apply call "
"(DataFrame or Series) in output_type."
msgstr ""
"在确定输出数据类型和返回值形状时，MaxFrame 会尝试将 ``func`` 应用于一个"
"模拟的分组对象，此时 apply 调用可能会失败。如果发生这种情况，你需要在 "
"output_type 中指定 apply 调用的类型（DataFrame 或 Series）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:74 of
msgid ""
"For DataFrame output, you need to specify a list or a pandas Series as "
"``dtypes`` of output DataFrame. ``index`` of output can also be "
"specified."
msgstr ""
"对于 DataFrame 输出，需要指定一个列表或 pandas Series 作为输出 DataFrame "
"的 ``dtypes``。输出的 ``index`` 也可以指定。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.apply.groupby_apply:77 of
msgid ""
"For Series output, you need to specify ``dtype`` and ``name`` of output "
"Series."
msgstr "对于 Series 输出，您需要指定输出 Series 的 ``dtype`` 和 ``name``。"

